OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BSUPER PAGE 58 IN 2023         W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BWhen I last wrote something for Chunky 
OL,8,BText, at the firstEChunky FringeBin    
OL,9,B2019, Super Page 58 had only been back 
OL,10,Bwith regular updates after its reboot  
OL,11,Bfor a little over a year.              
OL,13,BA lot was added to SP58 in that first  
OL,14,Byear back. Most significantly of all,  
OL,15,Bthe 2019 Digitiser Live came quickly   
OL,16,Bafter the launch of theEDigitiser Vault
OL,17,B- the first (and so far only) fully-   
OL,18,Borganised archive of recovered Digi    
OL,19,Bpages.                                 
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````1/9``
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10602
SC,0002
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BSUPER PAGE 58 IN 2023         W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,EThe Digitiser VaultBwent live on Super 
OL,8,BPage 58 on 11 May 2019. It launched    
OL,9,Bwith 570 editions of Digi represented  
OL,10,Bin its archives. This meant aroundE19% 
OL,11,Bof broadcast Digitiser editions had at 
OL,12,Bleast one page saved for posterity.    
OL,14,BLittle did I know, things were about to
OL,15,Bbe turbo-charged.                      
OL,17,BWith exquisite timing, recovery heroes 
OL,18,BlikeEAndrew NileBandETim Bisley        
OL,19,Bimmediately began sending their finds. 
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````2/9``
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10603
SC,0003
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BSUPER PAGE 58 IN 2023         W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BLaunching an archive with nearly 20% of
OL,8,Ba long-lost magazine represented is a  
OL,9,Bpretty good start - especially when    
OL,10,Bbest estimates show there were around  
OL,11,E3,000 editionsBof Digi during its      
OL,12,BTeletext run.                          
OL,14,BIn the four years since, the teletext  
OL,15,Brecovery scene has exploded. The halls 
OL,16,Bof the Digitiser Vault now play host to
OL,17,E47,995 pages,BfromE1,637 editions.     
OL,18,BThat's almost 55%! We've archived 35%  
OL,19,Bin four years. Let that sink in.       
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````3/9``
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10604
SC,0004
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BSUPER PAGE 58 IN 2023         W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BI take my metaphorical hat off to      
OL,8,Beveryone involved in theEteletext      
OL,9,Brecovery sceneB- what they do staggers 
OL,10,Bme. Their hard work, generosity, and   
OL,11,Bdedication are all humbling. The       
OL,12,Bcommunity spirit inspiring. TheEDigi   
OL,13,Earchives flourishBthanks to them.      
OL,15,BFrom an obscure, niche hobby, to...    
OL,16,Bwell, still an obscure and niche hobby 
OL,17,B- but now with many more people        
OL,18,Binvolved, and more tapes being         
OL,19,Bplundered for their riches than ever.  
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````4/9``
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10605
SC,0005
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BSUPER PAGE 58 IN 2023         W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BI rediscoveredEDigitiserBin 2016 when  
OL,8,EMr BiffoBheld Digifest at the Centre   
OL,9,BFor Computing History in Cambridge. At 
OL,10,Bthe same time, I learnt thatEteletext  
OL,11,ErecoveryBwas possible. How, I had no   
OL,12,Bidea - all I knew was that all of these
OL,13,Blost wonders were somehow viewable     
OL,14,Bagain.                                 
OL,16,BI never dreamed that the amount of     
OL,17,Bpages we'd gather would be getting on  
OL,18,BforEfifty thousand.BNearly all of what 
OL,19,BI call Digi's "grails" have been found.
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````5/9``
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10606
SC,0006
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BSUPER PAGE 58 IN 2023         W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BSometimes I wonder if our fineErecovery
OL,8,EheroesBappreciate just how grateful I  
OL,9,Bam, as a Digi fan of 30 years standing,
OL,10,Bfor what they've given us. It's a gift 
OL,11,Bto be able to see this stuff once more.
OL,13,EThe Man's assassination?BThe election  
OL,14,Bfor his replacement, and their eventual
OL,15,Bmetamorphosis back into The Man? All   
OL,16,BtheEfake ads,Bcelebrity pin-ups,       
OL,17,Bbizarre characters, andEprank phone    
OL,18,Ecalls?BWasn't it all a fever dream? No 
OL,19,B- and we can enjoy it all again.       
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````6/9``
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
