OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BSUPER PAGE 58 IN 2023         W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BThe otherEmajor additionBto Super Page 
OL,8,B58 was another epic labour of love.    
OL,9,BTaking 18 months to prepare for launch,
OL,10,BI added aEreviews archiveBin Feb 2022. 
OL,12,BIt's updated with reviews whenever     
OL,13,Bnewly-recovered editions of Digi are   
OL,14,Badded to the Vault - which is often!   
OL,16,BThere areEthousands of reviewsBwithin, 
OL,17,Band even more games rated, spanning one
OL,18,Bof the most significant eras for       
OL,19,Bgaming:Fhttps://is.gd/WiXfdv           
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````7/9``
OL,21,             BBy Chris Bell             
OL,22,D]MG    TELETEXT ART SHOWCASE p104      
OL,24,AAboutBUser GuideCTeletext ArtFMainIndex
PN,10608
SC,0008
FL,102,103,104,101,4ff,100
OL,1,U5|j5pp0up`pp0s1z0ppp      W h54  j  
OL,2,U5j5{57js15k!w      W 5$  j  
OL,3,U}~5|4}h|55j }|      Wh2-l|,&  
OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W*7<=mE`
OL,5,BSUPER PAGE 58 IN 2023         W!/////  
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7,BI self-evidently haven't been able to  
OL,8,Bdo all of this on my own. If it wasn't 
OL,9,Bfor theEkindness and generosityBof a   
OL,10,Bwhole team of people, I'd have been    
OL,11,Boverwhelmed by the size of the task.   
OL,13,BSome of theseEsuperstarsBhave chosen to
OL,14,Bremain anonymous, while others simply  
OL,15,Bdo it out of a sense of public service.
OL,17,BIt's that feeling of duty that I share 
OL,18,Bwith them: we do it all for you.EEnjoy!
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````8/9``
